Ana Battlemage.Rules:
Kicker {2}{U} and/or {1}{B}
When Ana Battlemage comes into play, if the {2}{U} kicker cost was paid, target player discards three cards.
When Ana Battlemage comes into play, if the {1}{B} kicker cost was paid, tap target untapped creature and that creature deals damage equal to its power to its controller.

Anavolver.Rules:
Kicker {1}{U} and/or {B}
If the {1}{U} kicker cost was paid, Anavolver comes into play with two +1/+1 counters on it and with flying.
If the {B} kicker cost was paid, Anavolver comes into play with a +1/+1 counter on it and with "Pay 3 life: Regenerate Anavolver."

Ancestral Knowledge.Rules:
Cumulative upkeep {1}
When Ancestral Knowledge comes into play, look at the top ten cards of your library, then remove any number of them from the game and put the rest back on top of your library in any order.
When Ancestral Knowledge leaves play, shuffle your library.

Argentum Armor.Rules:
Equipped creature gets +6/+6.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, destroy target permanent.
Equip {6}

Avacyn's Collar.Rules:
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has vigilance.
Whenever equipped creature dies, if it was a Human, put a 1/1 white Spirit creature token with flying onto the battlefield.
Equip {2}
